data.description: Welcome home to this charming single story that has been meticulously maintained and shows pride of ownership.  Nestled in the heart of the sought after Copper Basin community that offers top-notch amenities including Pool, Spa, Clubhouse, Workout Facility, Play Areas and lots of Walking and Hiking Trails.  Spacious and modern, this energy-efficient 3-bed, 2-bath home spans 1,778 square feet. The large kitchen with a generous island that has been custom designed for extra seating, granite countertops and an abundance of cabinets for ample storage opens to the dining area or bonus room. The open concept living room seamlessly integrates with the kitchen creating an airy and inviting space. This home prioritizes efficiency, with features such as Dual Pane Low E-Windows, Insulation, an HVAC Systems, Smart Home Connect System, Taexx built-in Pest Control System, reducing environmental impact while keeping utility costs lower. Over $16,000 in upgrades that include: Custom Laundry Cabinets, RO System, Stucco Backyard Wall, Extended Patio, Home Security System, Roof Gutters and Below Ground Drainage, Tile in Walkways and more.  The backyard has plenty of room with no two story homes behind for added privacy and an extended patio. Enjoy the perfect blend of comfort, style, and sustainability in this remarkable home.  This a house you will love to call home.
